# DataTidy23RodoSTA2005SAssignment

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of DataTidy23RodoSTA2005SAssignment is to create data for the STA2005S regression assignment in 2023.

## Installation

You can install the development version of DataTidy23RodoSTA2005SAssignment like so:

``` r
if (!requireNamespace("devtools")) install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("TRUE/DataTidy23RodoSTA2005SAssignment")
```
